revision.text: Possibly: Tatler (London, England : 1709): The lucubrations of Isaac Bickerstaff, Esq; 4 v. (Glasgow : Printed and sold by Robert Foulis, M DCC XLVII [1747-1749]). First published as "The tatler". Isaac Bickerstaff = Steele, Addison and others. Vols. 1-4 contain a reprint of 271 numbers from 12 April 1709 to 2 January 1710/11.
